name: The Feed
overview: In the near future, people’s minds are connected to The Feed, giving them instant connectivity. When something or someone invades it, everyone is at risk.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: In the near future, people’s minds are connected to The Feed, giving them instant connectivity. When something or someone invades The Feed, it’s creator must the seek the help of his estranged son.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Concerns about Kate’s behavior lead her and Tom to uncover a horrifying invasion of their family’s privacy.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Tom and Kate escape the city and join Max and Evelyn at a digital detox farm, but is all as idyllic as it seems?

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Tom turns to his father to save Max. Kate tries to find a doctor to remove their Feeds but comes up against the Resisters.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: When Tom and Kate make an alarming discovery about Bea, they confront Lawrence and Meredith at a family dinner which exposes long held secrets.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Lawrence pushes harder to discover the truth about what is happening to The Feed with devastating consequences for the Hatfield family.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: With the Takers coming through in increasing numbers, Tom and Kate take decisive but opposing actions. Lawrence leaves one last slight for Ben.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Ben spirals out of control when his actions have fatal consequences. Tom discovers he needs Ben’s help to stop the Takers, but can he find him in time?

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: As Tom and Ben get closer to solving the mystery of the Takers, Kate and Martha are locked in a desperate struggle for survival.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Tom and Ben fight with catastrophic consequences. Can Tom save his daughter and reunite with Kate before it’s too late?
